      "span_text": "An alternative method one can propose would be to partition the graph into many non-overlapping subgraphs S 1, S 2,., S t (using for example the highly scalable Louvain method for community detection in graphs ), compute an optimal solutionŜ i for each subgraph via any of the available methods, and finally piece together all local solutions by running a final synchronization algorithm on the new graph H whose nodes h i correspond to subgraphs S i."
